  в•‘  There are exactly THREE meta-equations:                          в•‘
  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
  в•‘  (I)   H(T) = I(О©(T), 2)     вЂ” the OCF                         в•‘
  в•‘        "Counting = Evaluation" вЂ” connects Levels 0,1,2           в•‘
  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
