  в•‘        "Homology = Triviality" вЂ” connects Levels 1,3              в•‘
  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
  в•‘  (III) e^{iПЂ} + 1 = 0         вЂ” the Euler identity               в•‘
  в•‘        "Growth Г— Rotation Г— Closure + Unity = Nothing"           в•‘
  в•‘        вЂ” connects Levels 4,5,6                                    в•‘
  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
  в•‘  Equation (I) IS Equation (III) restricted to tournament theory:  в•‘
  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
  в•‘  e = exponential growth of H with n                              в•‘
