  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
  в•‘  ОІв‚‚ = 0 for tournaments is LITERALLY в€‚ВІ = 0:                    в•‘
  в•‘  the chain complex в€‚в‚ѓв€‚в‚‚ = 0 forces ОІв‚‚ = ker(в€‚в‚‚)/im(в€‚в‚ѓ) = 0.   в•‘
  в•‘  The universal tournament vanishing IS the universal math law.   в•‘
  в•‘                                                                   в•‘
  в•‘  2 and 7:                                                         в•‘
